A vintage travel poster style illustration depicting a compact electronic device surrounded by an array of international airline tickets, foreign currency, and a well-worn leather passport on a wooden hotel desk. In the background, a window reveals an airplane silhouette against a warm sunset sky with layered clouds in muted oranges and teals. Multiple small glowing connection lines emanate from the central device, arcing gracefully toward tiny iconic landmarks from different countries scattered around the composition's edges. The color palette uses faded mustard yellows, dusty blues, and warm sepia tones with subtle paper texture overlay, evoking mid-century travel advertisements and the romance of international business travel.
